                    <comment id="12987746" author="shaie" created="Thu, 27 Jan 2011 20:42:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;MockRandom randomly set termsIndexDivisor. Changed it to set it only if it&apos;s not already -1, in which case we know someone specifically asked not to load the terms index (such as the test).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch includes the fix in MockRandomCodec and removes MockRandom from the set of illegal codecs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
